OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny rain and
OL,6,Fheavy showers soon clearing into the
OL,7,Fevening with clear spells developing.
OL,8,FCloud then thickens again from the
OL,9,Fwest through the early hours of
OL,10,FThursday, but likely staying dry.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FSome warm, sunny spells are
OL,13,Fexpected, but with cloud also building
OL,14,Fto bring occasional showers, heavy at
OL,15,Ftimes. Winds becoming light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
